created pseudo backdrop and grounded function

Three important things were done in this commit:

1) Created background and realistic “ground” for avatar
2) Avatar is able to detect ground, and player cannot start moving the
avatar unless the avatar is grounded.
3) Avatar is able to stop motion when keys aren’t being pressed.

created pseudo backdrop and grounded function

Three important things were done in this commit:

1) Created background and realistic “ground” for avatar
2) Avatar is able to detect ground, and player cannot start moving the
avatar unless the avatar is grounded.
3) Avatar is able to stop motion when keys aren’t being pressed.
